edulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"2794455140","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2794455140","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjc5NDQ1NTE0MA==","status":"current","title":"Metodologías de Trabajo","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":846},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2794455140/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2794455140/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2794455140/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2794455140/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2794455140","tinyui":"/x/ZACQpg","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2794455140","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2794455140/Metodolog+as+de+Trabajo","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2794455140"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p>Ahora que sos parte de Bancard, es hora de hablar de c&oacute;mo hacemos las cosas por ac&aacute;, especialmente en desarrollo. Esta parte del onboarding es como un mapa: te vamos a mostrar las herramientas, los procesos y todo lo que necesitas para trabajar bien en nuestros proyectos.</p><p>Primero, vamos a ver las tecnolog&iacute;as con las que trabajamos, desde los lenguajes de programaci&oacute;n hasta c&oacute;mo protegemos nuestros datos, todo tiene su porqu&eacute; en Bancard.</p><p>Luego, te vamos a contar sobre nuestro estilo de trabajo. Somos un equipo grande, y para que todo marche bien, seguimos un m&eacute;todo &aacute;gil. Te vamos a mostrar c&oacute;mo configuramos nuestros ambientes de desarrollo, staging y producci&oacute;n, para que sepas d&oacute;nde y c&oacute;mo hacer tu magia.</p><p>Lo m&aacute;s importante es que ac&aacute; en Bancard trabajamos juntos. Aunque somos muchos, cada uno aporta algo &uacute;nico. Por eso, la comunicaci&oacute;n y el apoyo son claves. En esta secci&oacute;n, vas a aprender c&oacute;mo colaboramos entre todos y c&oacute;mo nos aseguramos de que todo lo que hacemos est&eacute; bien organizado y sea de calidad.</p><p>As&iacute; que, prep&aacute;rate para empezar \uD83D\uDE0E Vas a aprender un mont&oacute;n y tambi&eacute;n vas a tener la oportunidad de aportar tus ideas y habilidades \uD83D\uDE80<br /></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"1024\" ac:original-width=\"1024\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:width=\"600\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20231128-201100.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p /><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1mgK7uaLlQPvZuZ17K0ZD7ORi-ANmpcMSXcr2sZeFoOg/edit#slide=id.g22abaddedca_0_68\" data-card-appearance=\"block\">https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1mgK7uaLlQPvZuZ17K0ZD7ORi-ANmpcMSXcr2sZeFoOg/edit#slide=id.g22abaddedca_0_68</a><hr /><p><em>Siguiente Paso &rarr; </em></p><ac:link ac:card-appearance=\"block\"><ri:page ri:content-title=\"Hosts Configuration\" ri:version-at-save=\"12\" /><ac:link-body>Hosts Configuration</ac:link-body></ac:link><p>  </p>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2269675523"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":528593318},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2269675523/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2269675523/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2269675523/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2269675523/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2269675523","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2269675523/Proceso+de+Desarrollo","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2269675523","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2269675523","tinyui":"/x/A4BIhw","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}